You swing both weapons, but you don't always hit with both weapons.   There's been plenty of times that I miss with my main hand and hit with the off hand and vice-versa<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>• You automatically do half damage with each weapon<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
